{"tid":2127355,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"末世景象 - 顏純鈎","createTime":"2020-07-27T09:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T10:52:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb0bc29f9693fc8804dcdcddbe3fbcb44ecfd33","tid":2127355,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:27:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A1%8F%E7%B4%94%E9%88%8E/daily/article/20200727/20963799/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A1%258F%25E7%25B4%2594%25E9%2588%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200727%2F20963799%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpb%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=065d451c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A1%258F%25E7%25B4%2594%25E9%2588%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200727%2F20963799%2F&h=0591b3a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A1%8F%E7%B4%94%E9%88%8E/daily/article/20200727/20963799/</a><br />\n<br />\n末世景象 - 顏純鈎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200727/large/1595749240_a72f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200727%2Flarge%2F1595749240_a72f.jpg&h=5755d255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸水災災情嚴重，但這一次，香港沒有捐款熱潮。黃絲不捐也罷了，藍絲也不捐，愛國心很可疑。<br />\n<br />\n國家在危難中，作為忠貞愛國者，豈可如此冷漠？捐多捐少不要緊，連作作樣子的動機都沒有，實在說不過去。<br />\n<br />\n董建華、梁振英這兩個政協副主席，貴為國家領導人，應該起個帶頭作用。董建華有百億身家，梁振英至少有五千萬來歷可疑的進帳，略表寸心只不過舉手之勞。此外，通過「香港再出發大聯盟」這個大平台，連接城中眾多大老闆慷慨解囊，至少十億百億拿出來，大鑼大鼓宣揚愛國心，有一舉兩得之妙。可惜至今毫無動靜，有負黨國眷顧之心。<br />\n<br />\n佔香港人口四成以上的藍絲，。。。。。。。。。。。。，日日撳住荷包。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。，九千萬黨員每人捐一百塊錢，就是九十億了，可惜九千萬黨員都裝聾作啞。<br />\n<br />\n政府救災懶懶閒。。。。。。。。。。。。。。惟有無語問蒼天。<br />\n<br />\n最近落馬的山西金融管理局長竟暉，居然家藏四億現金，如此大氣魄，叫小百姓如何承受？。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n國事蜩螗，內外交煎，官員怠政，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。錢沒有了，能指望共產主義的偉大理想？<br />\n<br />\n江山在飄搖中，人民在苦難裏，如何收場，惟有天知。 <br />\n<br />\n顏純鈎"},{"pid":"14b72ace29f79300e29bc3258d9cc27e56c5bb09","tid":2127355,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"梁振英至少有五千萬來歷可疑的進帳，略表寸心只不過舉手之勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5e3711ea54e059b0d78570f7717ca7cdb60c28","tid":2127355,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"支持國安法嘅人去咗邊"}]}